      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections, such as light surface scratches or slight interior wear, consistent with regular use. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
