    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response across the entire power band. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers short, precise throws, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the car is flawless: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced as a preventative measure, and the rod bearings have been addressed with documented service history. The suspension geometry remains stock, featuring fresh bushings and OEM dampers for a period-correct, communicative ride. The exterior paint retains its factory luster with no swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior Nappa leather shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
